 RELEASE 0.6.4
---------------

- Log4j appender revised so that it is fully configurable through an
  standard log4j properties configuration file.

- Scoja clients work with jdk1.3.

- Sources (both inet and unix) are a bit more robust.
  If an error occurs while opening the socket, it keeps retrying.
  shouldStop signal works now correctly with tcp source.

- A few details concerning internal events tags.
  Now, all events has a tag with at least 3 parts (syslog.scoja.*[...]).

- New function "instance" to access template capabilities.
